
Script 1. Generates figures describing:

- most common tests reported by laboratories
- number of behavioral tests performed per subject
- reasoning for test order
- prevalence of multiple tests performed on the same day

---

### Literature analysis

Script 2. Generates figures describing:

- most frequently used behavioral assays in NTT studies
- most commonly reported behavioral parameters
- number of tests per study
- co-occurrence patterns between behavioral assays

---

## Reproducibility

All analyses were performed in **R**.

Required packages: tidyverse
readxl
janitor
stringr
tidytext
patchwork
scico
